{"tid":573971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"自稱IS分支成員　fb轉載劫獄案","createTime":"2018-02-27T03:26:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-27T13:16:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a23c7b16e67651e0f8be57ae89d33581b036c9d6","tid":573971,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:26:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180227/20316905\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180227%2F20316905&d=u9aNrW9w0vJ2xZCPsOckSXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=8d691e8a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180227%2F20316905&h=e0a53587\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180227/20316905</a><br />\n<br />\n自稱IS分支成員　fb轉載劫獄案<br />\n<br />\n頭條   <br />\n         <br />\n【本報訊】消息稱落網的Ramanjit在香港的南亞圈相當活躍，早年縱橫重慶大廈，幾乎無人不識，其後他更遭本地黑幫招攬，活躍於東九龍及土瓜灣一帶。據悉，有人曾向同鄉聲稱自己為極端恐怖組織伊斯蘭國（IS）香港分支成員，同鄉都對他敬畏三分。<br />\n<br />\nRamanjit在香港的「控制室」設在土瓜灣浙江街一間劏房單位，原由他與前女友租住，兩人育有一對子女（現年6歲及2歲），其後二人分手，長子跟他，由其居於彩虹邨的家人照顧，幼女則隨母親生活。據悉，他有定期到上址探望女兒，並不時在facebook（fb）分享與子女一起的相片。<br />\n其fb亦顯示他不時與家鄉的親友通訊，並在網上分享同胞手持獵槍的照片，每當有家鄉的「兄弟」生日，他都會送上遙遠的祝福。去年3月當地傳媒報道有關轟動印度的劫獄案時，更立即在fb上轉載。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黃祺文<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180227/large/1519667331_59f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180227%2Flarge%2F1519667331_59f9.jpg&h=1d6c87eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n疑犯在fb上載同胞持獵槍照。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t印度可要求引渡回國受審<br />\n頭條 6小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t港劏房作控制室　策劃恐怖活動劫案疑犯　指揮印度黨羽殺人劫獄<br />\n頭條 6小時前"},{"pid":"b2511810e1ad85826606f9cbdef33cf8035031af","tid":573971,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:42:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"755afa69af445b056e800921768c20856a3a2301","tid":573971,"uid":119494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T07:07:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝難民之父<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c179c4a92e664e4602b55ee1fb5083406b379efd","tid":573971,"uid":71257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T07:18:26.000Z","msg":"係香港坐監姐係益佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n納稅人都哂錢養班死差仔<br />\n<br />\n希望柳記玩殘佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b43d2dd9efcd5de44bd86d62363c56dae298546c","tid":573971,"uid":113626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T07:19:57.000Z","msg":"連IS都有老婆仔女<br />\n你叫連登仔點面對 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ab71917ca6b6f5826b080597eeb7b294c0ba71","tid":573971,"uid":71257,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T07:20:53.000Z","msg":"希望佢長子 幼女 同彩虹邨嘅屋企人死於非命<br />\n<br />\n香港唔歡迎你班死差仔"},{"pid":"f5d336cc3e87f07e88b9275eddd431d7ee5daae7","tid":573971,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T07:38:43.000Z","msg":"唔係錫克教徒咩？"},{"pid":"98924dedcaa3eb397581e0117a699121e856a6a5","tid":573971,"uid":89797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c179c4a92e664e4602b55ee1fb5083406b379efd","tid":573971,"uid":71257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T07:18:26.000Z","msg":"係香港坐監姐